    'description' => 'Monitor product prices from e-commerce pages. Given a URL and a price selector (CSS or XPath), fetches the page periodically, extracts the price, stores the history in SQLite, and reports price changes/drops. Uses DOMDocument/DOMXPath for HTML parsing and PDO_SQLite for persistence. First e-commerce/market data capability in the ecosystem. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
    'parameters' => 
